1
00:00:00,041 --> 00:00:05,125
We will enter the prison compound, and here, of course, is the vehicle entrance

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:07,000
Into the basement

3
00:00:08,083 --> 00:00:09,083
And the first step

4
00:00:11,333 --> 00:00:12,666
In the prison procedure

5
00:00:14,666 --> 00:00:19,458
You go down, and the vehicles drive into
the basement. This area was the car garage

6
00:00:19,958 --> 00:00:26,000
For the prisoners’ transport vehicles,
and for the guards’ and interrogators’ cars

7
00:00:27,041 --> 00:00:29,458
This whole section, of course, was a parking area

8
00:00:30,333 --> 00:00:31,625
Sometimes a person would be taken out

9
00:00:32,625 --> 00:00:37,666
They would take him out of prison, and if his eyes were
not blindfolded, he would notice the prisoners’ vehicles

10
00:00:38,208 --> 00:00:39,458
Someone might recognize them

11
00:00:40,791 --> 00:00:44,000
And this is the door to the
investigation room and the group cells

12
00:00:44,458 --> 00:00:47,375
And this is the main prison gate

13
00:00:48,333 --> 00:00:52,666
We enter through here, and the first room is the
custody room, which was also the investigation room

14
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,041
We go to the right side, where the
solitary cells and group cells are located

15
00:00:59,791 --> 00:01:01,708
And on the left side, there is a kitchen belonging to them

16
00:01:02,416 --> 00:01:04,750
And there is a hidden group cell

17
00:01:05,416 --> 00:01:07,333
And there is a regular group cell
